{"word":"G5248 - ὑπερπερισσεύω - hyperperisseúō - hoop-er-per-is-syoo'-o - Abound much more","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑπερπερισσεύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hyperperisseúō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hoop-er-per-is-syoo'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Abound much more</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அதிகமாய்ப் பெருகு, பரிபூரணமாயிரு"},{"paragraph":"to abound beyond measure, abound exceedingly"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5228 - ὑπέρ - hypér - hoop-er'/5228\">G5228</a> and <a href=\"#/G4052 - περισσεύω - perisseúō - per-is-syoo'-o/4052\">G4052</a>; to <i>super abound:</i> - abound much more, exceeding.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G4050/4050\">G4050</a>, <a href=\"#/G4051/4051\">G4051</a>, <a href=\"#/G4052/4052\">G4052</a>, <a href=\"#/G4053/4053\">G4053</a>, <a href=\"#/G4057/4057\">G4057</a>, <a href=\"#/G5248/5248\">G5248</a>, <a href=\"#/G5249/5249\">G5249</a>"}]}